session.gui
Class ForroSim

java.lang.Object
  session.gui.ForroSim

public final class ForroSim
extends java.lang.Object

Runnable class for all simulations.

Program arguments: "-rmi" or "globus"

VM arguments: -Djava.rmi.server.hostname="this hostname" -Dforro.model.packagename="models package name"

Author:
Simfra team.
